\overline{B}:=\prod_{i=1}^{n}[a_{i},b_{i}]:=\left\{ (x_{1},...,x_{n}):x_{i}\in[a_{i},b_{i}],\forall\,i=1,...,n\right\} \subset\mathbb{R}^{n}\label{eq:n-维闭区间}
