\begin_layout Definition*
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[开覆盖]
\end_layout

\end_inset

对于 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{R}^{n}$
\end_inset

 的任意子集 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

，如果有 
\begin_inset Formula $A\subset\bigcup_{k\in K}B_{k}$
\end_inset

，其中指标集 
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

 至多可数，且 
\begin_inset Formula $B_{k}$
\end_inset

 均为 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

-维开区间，则称 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ B_{k}\right\} _{k\in K}$
\end_inset

 是 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 的一个「开覆盖（Open Cover）」。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
显然：满足
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand nameref
reference "axm:测度"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

公理的 
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

 应当确保
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
m(A)\le m\left(\bigcup_{k\in K}B_{k}\right)\le\sum_{k\in K}m(B_{k})=\sum_{k\in K}v(B_{k})
\]

\end_inset

这里的不等号引用了「可数次可加性」。由此可以引出
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
m(A)\le\inf\left\{ \sum_{k\in K}v(B_{k}):\left(\abs{K}\le\aleph_{0}\right)\land\left(A\subset\bigcup_{k\in K}B_{k}\right)\right\} 
\]

\end_inset

右端的下确界是一个由点集 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 确定的非负实数，因此可以被定义为一种「测度」：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[外测度]
\end_layout

\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "def:外测度"

\end_inset


\begin_inset Index idx
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
measure!outer ~
\end_layout

\end_inset

对于 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{R}^{n}$
\end_inset

 的任意子集 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

，它的「外测度（Outer Measure）」 是指
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
m^{*}(A):=\inf\left\{ \sum_{k\in K}v(B_{k}):\left(\abs{K}\le\aleph_{0}\right)\land\left(A\subset\bigcup_{k\in K}B_{k}\right)\right\} 
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $B_{k}$
\end_inset

 均为 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

-维开区间。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
可以验证：
\end_layout

\begin_layout Lemma
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand nameref
reference "def:外测度"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

满足
